            <div class="entry-problem"><p class="para0" style="text-align:left;">(라)의 ㉢에 담긴 용이의 심정으로 적절하지 <span style="text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-color:black;">않은</span> 것은?</p><div class="level4"><div class="sel_list"><p class="para0" style="text-align:left;"><span class="sel_num_po">① </span>설렘</p></div><div class="sel_list"><p class="para0" style="text-align:left;"><span class="sel_num_po">② </span>감사함</p></div><div class="sel_list"><p class="para0" style="text-align:left;"><span class="sel_num_po">③ </span>고소함</p></div><div class="sel_list"><p class="para0" style="text-align:left;"><span class="sel_num_po">④ </span>통쾌함</p></div><div class="sel_list"><p class="para0" style="text-align:left;"><span class="sel_num_po">⑤ </span>후련함</p></div></div></div>
